                <div class="jonra" data-uuid="941d48c967124dfebd6f733a2fd80cd8">
                    <h2 data-uuid="daa427ee1b1b4cdc9fc6619865023713">Anti-Abolitionist Rally</h2>
                    <p class="source" data-uuid="defb9296ee4645a191dd31ba197f34d6">Members of an anti-abolitionist group used this flyer to call people together in order to disrupt a meeting of abolitionists in 1837.</p>
